  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Expand Your Storage Options",
      "text": "The Ubiquiti M.2 SSD Tray (UACC-SSD-Tray) is a compact, high-quality storage accessory designed for the Cloud Gateway Max and Cloud Gateway Fiber. It allows you to integrate one M.2 NVMe SSD of sizes 2230, 2242, 2260, 2280, or 22110 to enhance your device’s storage capacity. With support for PCIe Gen3 x2 lanes, this tray ensures optimal performance for high-speed data operations. While all M.2 NVMe SSDs are supported, they will operate within the Gen3x2 performance limits of the host device. Constructed from durable aluminum alloy, polycarbonate, and stainless steel, the tray offers excellent heat dissipation and long-term reliability. Lightweight yet sturdy, the tray is an ideal solution for expanding storage without compromising space or performance."
    },
    {
      "heading": "",
      "text": "",
