        "alt": "/images/catalogue/description/2709/picture2-688088c47dfb4-1252x465.jpg"
      }
    },
    {
      "heading": "Durable & Reliable",
      "text": "Engineered for seamless integration, the UACC-SSD-Tray brings flexibility and simplicity to your storage expansion needs. Its robust aluminum alloy housing protects your NVMe SSD while maintaining a sleek and compact profile that fits neatly within your Cloud Gateway setup. The tray supports M.2 NVMe SSDs across multiple form factors, offering compatibility with 2230 through 22110 sizes. Designed to pair perfectly with Ubiquiti’s Cloud Gateway Max and Fiber devices, it enhances storage while ensuring consistent performance for data-intensive applications. Installation is straightforward, requiring no additional tools or complex setup. Whether you’re optimizing your network infrastructure or scaling storage for enterprise use, the UACC-SSD-Tray delivers a dependable and efficient solution. It is ideal for keeping server racks organized and professional."
    },
